data.title: What popular Irish songs should I know for celebrating St. Patrick’s Day?
data.meta_description:
Answer (1 of 8): First, Happy St Patrick’s Day from Ireland.

Ballads are extremely popular, 4 of the following 5 are Compulsory Learning;

 * The Irish Rover, written by Joseph M Crofts, a hit for the Dubliners & Pogues in the 1980s - Learn off by heart
